# ==============================================================================
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3
*.db
*.db-journal
*.sql
*.dump
*.bak
/pgdata/
/postgres-data/
# Note: Your compiled public/bible-points.parquet is safe to push as it is 
# public historical data required by the static Next.js frontend.

